      "text": "サニピー！　サニピー！",
      "startTime": 30.3333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 33.1166625498
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 33.1166625498
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03-szk005.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃーーーーん！　Fuー！！\nやばいやばいいつもの髪型も可愛いけどこっちも最高！",
      "startTime": 37.5666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 37.5666662852
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 41.1666638214
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと雫、芽衣、関係者席なんだから\n立ったら目立つわよ。もう、渚達も夢中になってるし",
      "startTime": 44.5333329518,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 50.6999969005
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "え～？　でも怜ちゃんだって、サニピ！　サニピ！\nって声出してたよ？　我慢しなくていいってば～",
      "startTime": 54.7666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 59.7333299796
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "ま、まぁ、出してはいたけど……それだけ、ほら……\n本当に立派で、眩しいくらいだから……",
      "startTime": 66.2666662852,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 66.2666662852
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 70.3999951203
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "（最初の頃は、体力もなくて……ランニングで遅れたり）\n（私のこと、厳しいって震えてたっけ。でも……）",
      "startTime": 76.1666647593,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_hillpark-00-night.webp",
      "bgName": "hillpark-00-night",
      "startTime": 82.2999991893
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "（陰ながら、コツコツ頑張って……全国ツアーも……）\n（無人島ロケも乗り越えて……千紗なりに、あんなに……）",
      "startTime": 87.4666688282,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ライブ終了後",
      "startTime": 96.2000052134,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1633.3333333000014,
          "startTime": 97.8333385467
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3899.9999999999914,
          "startTime": 100.1000052134
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_door-open-02.m4a",
          "delay": 1433.3328247000027,
          "startTime": 97.6333380381
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_liveslope-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "3dgakuya",
      "startTime": 97.4000047047
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "千紗ちゃ～ん！　すっごく良かったよ～！\nもうほんとに、一人でも十人分ぐらいだった！",
      "startTime": 103.2333385467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03-chs008.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ、ありがとう。でも、まさかサプライズゲストで\nお姉ちゃんが来てくれるなんて、びっくりしたよ",
      "startTime": 112.8333385467,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 10133.333333300001,
          "startTime": 122.96667188
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
          "delay": 11233.333333299996,
          "startTime": 124.06667188
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03-chs009.m4a",
      "text": "あと、「あげるよ」とか一度歌ってみたいな～って\n思ってた部分が歌えて……って怜ちゃんどうしたの！？",
      "startTime": 121.6333385467,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "っ……千紗……千紗ぁ……っ……",
      "startTime": 126.5666648387,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03-chs010.m4a",
      "text": "ふぇ～！？　な、なんで泣いてるの？\nなんで急に抱きついてるの～！？",
      "startTime": 137.1666530609,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03-chs011.m4a",
      "text": "（お姉ちゃんだけじゃなくて、サニピのみんなだけ）\n（でもなくて。沢山の人のおかげで、今の私がいる）",
      "startTime": 146.3999721527,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03/sud_vo_adv_card_chs_53_03-chs012.m4a",
      "text": "（ふふ、たまにびっくりしちゃうこともあるけど）\n（――ありがとう、みんなと出会えた奇跡に）",
      "startTime": 157.4333014171,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}